#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.unique.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.unique"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:1 of
msgid "Find the unique elements of a tensor."
msgstr "查找张量中的唯一元素。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns the sorted unique elements of a tensor. There are three optional "
"outputs in addition to the unique elements:"
msgstr "返回张量中排序后的唯一元素。除了唯一元素外，还有三个可选输出："

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:6 of
msgid "the indices of the input tensor that give the unique values"
msgstr "输入张量中产生唯一值的索引"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:7 of
msgid "the indices of the unique tensor that reconstruct the input tensor"
msgstr "唯一张量中用于重构输入张量的索引"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:8 of
msgid "the number of times each unique value comes up in the input tensor"
msgstr "每个唯一值在输入张量中出现的次数"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:10 of
msgid ""
"Input tensor. Unless `axis` is specified, this will be flattened if it is"
" not already 1-D."
msgstr "输入张量。除非指定了 `axis`，否则如果不是一维的，它将被展平。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:13 of
msgid ""
"If True, also return the indices of `ar` (along the specified axis, if "
"provided, or in the flattened tensor) that result in the unique tensor."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则还返回 `ar` 的索引（沿指定轴，如果提供；或者在展平后的张量"
"中），这些索引可生成唯一张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:16 of
msgid ""
"If True, also return the indices of the unique tensor (for the specified "
"axis, if provided) that can be used to reconstruct `ar`."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则还返回唯一张量的索引（对于指定轴，如果提供），这些索引可"
"用于重构 `ar`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:19 of
msgid "If True, also return the number of times each unique item appears in `ar`."
msgstr "如果为 True，则还返回每个唯一项在 `ar` 中出现的次数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:22 of
msgid ""
"The axis to operate on. If None, `ar` will be flattened. If an integer, "
"the subarrays indexed by the given axis will be flattened and treated as "
"the elements of a 1-D tensor with the dimension of the given axis, see "
"the notes for more details.  Object tensors or structured tensors that "
"contain objects are not supported if the `axis` kwarg is used. The "
"default is None."
msgstr ""
"操作的轴。如果为 None，则 `ar` 将被展平。如果为整数，则由给定轴索引的子"
"数组将被展平，并视为具有给定轴维度的一维张量的元素，更多细节参见说明。"
"如果使用 `axis` 参数，则不支持包含对象的对象张量或结构化张量。默认值为 "
"None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:30 of
msgid ""
"* **unique** (*Tensor*) -- The sorted unique values. * **unique_indices**"
" (*Tensor, optional*) -- The indices of the first occurrences of the "
"unique values in the   original tensor. Only provided if `return_index` "
"is True. * **unique_inverse** (*Tensor, optional*) -- The indices to "
"reconstruct the original tensor from the   unique tensor. Only provided "
"if `return_inverse` is True. * **unique_counts** (*Tensor, optional*) -- "
"The number of times each of the unique values comes up in the   original "
"tensor. Only provided if `return_counts` is True."
msgstr ""
"* **unique** (*Tensor*) -- 排序后的唯一值。* **unique_indices** (*Tensor,"
" optional*) -- 唯一值在原始张量中首次出现的索引。仅当 `return_index` 为 "
"True 时提供。* **unique_inverse** (*Tensor, optional*) -- 从唯一张量重构"
"原始张量的索引。仅当 `return_inverse` 为 True 时提供。* **unique_counts**"
" (*Tensor, optional*) -- 每个唯一值在原始张量中出现的次数。仅当 `return_"
"counts` 为 True 时提供。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:30 of
msgid "**unique** (*Tensor*) -- The sorted unique values."
msgstr "**unique** (*Tensor*) -- 排序后的唯一值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:31 of
msgid ""
"**unique_indices** (*Tensor, optional*) -- The indices of the first "
"occurrences of the unique values in the original tensor. Only provided if"
" `return_index` is True."
msgstr ""
"**unique_indices** (*Tensor, optional*) -- 唯一值在原始张量中首次出现的"
"索引。仅当 `return_index` 为 True 时提供。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:33 of
msgid ""
"**unique_inverse** (*Tensor, optional*) -- The indices to reconstruct the"
" original tensor from the unique tensor. Only provided if "
"`return_inverse` is True."
msgstr ""
"**unique_inverse** (*Tensor, optional*) -- 用于从唯一张量重构原始张量的"
"索引。仅当 `return_inverse` 为 True 时提供。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:35 of
msgid ""
"**unique_counts** (*Tensor, optional*) -- The number of times each of the"
" unique values comes up in the original tensor. Only provided if "
"`return_counts` is True."
msgstr ""
"**unique_counts** (*Tensor, optional*) -- 每个唯一值在原始张量中出现的"
"次数。仅当 `return_counts` 为 True 时提供。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:39 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:48 of
msgid "Return the unique rows of a 2D tensor"
msgstr "返回二维张量的唯一行"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:54 of
msgid "Return the indices of the original tensor that give the unique values:"
msgstr "返回原始张量中生成唯一值的索引："

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.unique.unique:67 of
msgid "Reconstruct the input array from the unique values:"
msgstr "从唯一值重构输入数组："

